  "title": "Purchasing Assistant | Central |$2,300",
  "description": "<p><strong>Purchasing Assistant</strong><br />Location: Central<br />Working hours: Mon – Fri, 8am – 5.30pm</p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Collaborate with project and purchasing teams on material procurement, stock management, and payables for projects.</li><li>Manage the purchasing of materials for projects, including sourcing, invoicing, billing, stock control, and maintaining corresponding documentation in network folders.</li><li>Perform electronic filing of documentation and update schedules of values as needed.</li><li>Assist in the preparation and tracking of project budgeting and accounts payable.</li><li>Investigate and reconcile any invoicing, purchase order, or payment discrepancies.</li><li>Support the project management team with reporting and analysis as required.</li></ul><p><strong>Experience:</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience in a procurement position is preferable but not mandatory.</li><li><strong>OJT provided.</strong></li><li>Strong Excel skills are required.</li></ul><p><strong>Skills:</strong></p><ul><li>Ability to work independently and be self-motivated.</li><li>Capacity to understand the broader context, ask pertinent questions, and make recommendations.</li><li>Strong attention to detail, resourcefulness, and the ability to multitask.</li><li>A strong team player.</li></ul><p>Interested parties, please email to <em><strong>kyo@temp-team.com.sg</strong></em><br />Karin Yong<br />Registration: R22109239<br />EA Licence: 01C3135</p><p></p><p></p><p></p>",
